Usage: loadFPlan [-help] <file> [-noEqualizePtnHInst] [-objType <string>]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
<file>                       # fplan file name (string, required)
-noEqualizePtnHInst          # (bool, optional)
-objType <string>            # objects section in floor plan file you want to
                             # update: {macro | pin | bndry | special_route |
                             # pin_constraint} (string, optional)